metadata.name: IL DESIDERIO SEGRETO No1
metadata.description:
IL DESIDERIO SEGRETO 

One of my most famous works

2011
This work has been the design for more than 1,000 tattoos on the bodies of different people in different countries from 2011 until today.

I have about 800 of the best tattoos in my collection, based on 5 works from this series.

2012
Was on the cover of the magazine Bigshot (IT)

2013
Was on the cover of the digital magazine REtouched (US)

2011 / 4256x3234 / 300 dpi
Photographer: Jan Max
MUA: H. Arakelyan
Costume designer: Pallari
Model: Stella
